# Global Flutter agent reminder

Canon: `AGENTS.md` → `docs/agent_knowledge_base.md` → `docs/agent_project_context.md` → `docs/ai_code_review_protocol.md`. Commands: `docs/agents_quick_reference.md` only.

## Execution (beyond always-on map)

- Intent / spec / implementation stay separate (why+constraints vs eval contract vs repo tactics).
- Vague or risky: boundaries, data flow, failure handling, smallest verifiable slice before codegen.
- Loop: plan → tool → observe → revise; inspectable task state; empty or malformed tool output is not proof.
- Tool orchestration: repo scripts/tests, browser/app proof, MCP/connectors, code graph; prompts alone are not proof; name inputs, side effects, retry safety, failure modes.
- UI: `DESIGN.md` + `docs/design_system.md`; runtime tokens first; verify workflow, states, responsive no-overlap.

## Context budget

- Smallest reads; targeted search beats dumps.
- **context ladder:** map docs → durable memory → code-review-graph → targeted raw files.
- Refactor/feature audit: record only real landmines (bugs, workarounds, deprecated patterns).
- Compare approaches only when uncertainty/risk pays; default one path.

## Quality bar

- Reversible change for business goal + reliability bar.
- Don't edit until **95% confident** in goal/scope/approach.
- **Surgical diff:** each changed line traces to request or required validation/doc update.
- Validation scripts are gates; change scripts only for demonstrated false positives.
- AI output is draft until review passes; finish gate: edge cases, failures, ops, breakage impact.
- **Self-verify before report:** request, changed files, proof, blockers, residual risk.

## Repo-first

- Repo docs and shell entrypoints over host shortcuts.
- Repeated failure → doc, fixture, test, script, route proof, or validation check.
- **File verified reusable conclusions** → source doc, `docs/changes/`, `docs/plans/`, or `tasks/lessons.md` (not chat-only).
- Agent/docs edits: semantic-lint duplicates/stale plans; keep `AGENTS.md` short; run `./tool/check_agent_knowledge_base.sh`.
- Behavior changes: source docs first, then sync Codex/Cursor templates.
- `DESIGN.md` edits → `./tool/check_design_md.sh`; Mix → `./tool/run_mix_lint.sh`.
- Widget tests: [`docs/testing_overview.md`](docs/testing_overview.md) § Feature-defined testing; layout-sensitive sizing in [`docs/testing/widget_test_playbook.md`](docs/testing/widget_test_playbook.md) (not repo-wide `WidgetTester.view` until a harness exists). Never deprecated `tester.binding.window` APIs.
